    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements for a Class II CPB device. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the cardiopulmonary bypass clinical envelope described in the Claim and Requirement documentation.",
